Privacy Policy
Effective Date:
5/29/2023
Please read this Privacy Policy carefully before using the "Photo Collage Maker" app provided by [Your Company Name] ("we", "us", "our") designed for creating and editing photo collages. This Privacy Policy describes how our app collects and uses data from your device. It also outlines your rights and options regarding your personal information.
Information Collection and Use
1.1. Device Information: When you use our app, we may collect information about your device, including its unique identifier, operating system version, and network information. This data helps us optimize and enhance the performance of our app and troubleshoot any technical issues you may encounter.
1.2. Usage Data: We collect usage data, including interactions with the app, feature usage, and preferences. This data is anonymized and used for analytical purposes to understand user behavior, improve the quality of our app, and personalize your experience. It may also be used to generate aggregated statistical reports.
Camera and Photo Gallery Access
2.1. Camera Access: In order to create photo collages, our app requires access to your device's camera. This enables you to capture new photos directly within the app for use in your collages.
2.2. Photo Gallery Access: Our app also requires access to your device's photo gallery to select and import existing photos for use in your collages. We only access the photos that you specifically choose within the app.
Data Storage and Security
3.1. Data Storage: All data collected by our app is stored securely on your device and is not transmitted to our servers. We do not store any personal information or photos on our servers. However, please note that we cannot guarantee the security of data stored on your device.
3.2. Security: We take reasonable measures to protect the security of your data and prevent unauthorized access, loss, or disclosure. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure. We encourage you to take precautions to protect your personal information and use our app in a secure environment.
Third-Party Services
4.1. Third-Party Links: Our app may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these websites or services. We recommend reviewing their respective privacy policies before providing any personal information.
4.2. Third-Party Analytics: We may use third-party analytics services, such as Google Analytics, to gather usage statistics and insights. These services collect and analyze non-personal data to help us understand user behavior, improve our app, and measure the effectiveness of our marketing efforts.
Children's Privacy
Our app is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us, and we will promptly delete such information from our records.
Changes to the Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated Privacy Policy within the app or through other means. Your continued use of the app after the changes will signify your acceptance of the revised Privacy Policy.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at
greenbox.developer@gmail.com
By using the "Photo Collage Maker" app, you consent to the collection and use of your information as described in this Privacy Policy.
